{"tid":2063102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有支援手足組織被恐嚇！","createTime":"2020-06-13T15:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T02:35:20.000Z","uid":90282,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf2361b9773e06035f43f74a7d99bef9cfc218d","tid":2063102,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200613/UH6RCZGNSOPPVQTEUQCUWOYNII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FUH6RCZGNSOPPVQTEUQCUWOYNII%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=0358e106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FUH6RCZGNSOPPVQTEUQCUWOYNII%2F&h=a65ded06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200613/UH6RCZGNSOPPVQTEUQCUWOYNII/</a><br />\n<strong>【本報訊】反送中運動一周年，明暗打壓無所不在。有支援被捕者的義工近日收到疑似呈堂文件內頁，上面載有抗爭者被捕相片，並恐嚇說如繼續手上工作「下一個就係你」、「打完你再坐監」。義工估計有人知他們正籌備「警暴檔案」進行投訴，欲威脅噤聲，但他強調不會被嚇怕。大律師指相關文件僅警方及控辯持有，行為或涉恐嚇。律政司及警方稱相關人員需按嚴格守則處理訴訟文件，籲受恐嚇人士報警。 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家幫得幾多得幾多啦</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/100053201_256355482378142_4516874057022439424_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_oc=AQlN4uylggQUXMAlr0kGNnUStu7RWe8QHsu4vZx7Rcf1vGgsf8RIhMxHNTdYbG2yPpk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=811d62178b13361a1cb98f5258c6a7ca&amp;oe=5F0AAFA4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F100053201_256355482378142_4516874057022439424_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_oc%3DAQlN4uylggQUXMAlr0kGNnUStu7RWe8QHsu4vZx7Rcf1vGgsf8RIhMxHNTdYbG2yPpk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D811d62178b13361a1cb98f5258c6a7ca%26oe%3D5F0AAFA4&h=eb9a0d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Book/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=ht